Definition: a steroid hormone produced by the adrenal cortex or synthesized
Example: administered as drugs they reduce swelling and decrease the body's immune response; adrenal cortical steroids are used to treat many different conditions
Synonyms: corticoid, adrenal_cortical_steroid, steroid_hormone, a, steroid, hormone, produced, by, the, adrenal, cortex, or, synthesized, administered, as, drugs, they, reduce, swelling, and, decrease, body, s, immune, response, cortical, steroids, are, used, to, treat, many, different, conditions
Category: noun.substance
